{"tid":1121434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪個個都當自己係歌星？","createTime":"2019-04-23T10:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T12:59:54.000Z","uid":250001,"like":17,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9185976dbf801f2658ebd4f94d701cf405f6ed8","tid":1121434,"uid":250001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"早排喺度行吓行吓<br />\n突然聽到一把魔音好撚做作咁<br />\n屌原來有條女喺度busking<br />\n一開始望落去以為個細路女喺度唱歌 （身高）<br />\n所以唱到好似亂咁嚟咁<br />\n再望真啲條女真係嚇撚死我<br />\n<br />\n啲真音好似想震爆我個頭<br />\n啲假音好似好似想刺穿我啲耳膜<br />\n啲音都未去到 就走左<br />\n咬字完全正 都唔知佢唱乜柒<br />\n同殘酷一丁嘅「帶子」真係有得揮<br />\n<br />\n一開始諗係咪現場live show 所以臨時表現得唔好<br />\n跟住上埋佢IG睇 <br />\n我屌 真係唔知佢唱乜柒 <br />\n原本唱左咁多年都冇進步 <br />\n <br />\n然後仲有人comment話佢唱得好撚好聽<br />\n佢啲朋友真係好黑心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/lokyiuet?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=gc89ub6lys37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flokyiuet%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3Dgc89ub6lys37&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=dea3701a\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/lokyiuet?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=gc89ub6lys37</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BNG75zFAFec/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=4k16t292w4t0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBNG75zFAFec%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D4k16t292w4t0&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OD2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=77b77925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBNG75zFAFec%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D4k16t292w4t0&h=7de8fafd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BNG75zFAFec/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=4k16t292w4t0</a><br />\n真係聽到人 心亂如麻 燥鬱症發作 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BjmGljvF0NX/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=14r294lfet0s4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l